.TH compla 1 "October 1994" "Scilab Group" "Scilab Function"
.so man1/sci.an
.SH NAME 
compla - from adjacency pointer and node arrays to arc array
.SH CALLING SEQUENCE
.nf
[la] = compla(lp,ls,dir)
.fi
.SH PARAMETERS
.TP 3
la
: la is the arc array in the adjacency description
.TP 6
lp,ls
: vectors of the adjacency description, lp is the pointer array and 
  ls is the node array
.TP 4
dir
: integer flag, 1 if the graph is directed, 0 if the graph is 
  undirected
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fVcompla\fR computes the arc array in the adjacencency description from
the pointer array and the node array.
.SH SEE ALSO
compl2
